1. *Kazne* za prekoračenje brzine su veoma visoke. (Penalties for speeding are very high.)
2. Vlada je pooštrila *kazne* za kršenje mera protiv epidemije. (The government has increased penalties for violating measures against the epidemic.)
3. Sudija je odredio *kaznu* od pet godina zatvora za optuženog. (The judge sentenced the accused to five years in prison.)
4. Policajci su izrekli *kaznu* vozaču koji je vozio pod uticajem alkohola. (The police officers issued a fine to the driver who was driving under the influence of alcohol.)
5. *Kazne* za nepoštovanje saobraćajnih propisa mogu biti veoma ozbiljne. (Penalties for disregarding traffic regulations can be very serious.)
6. Advokat je savetovao svog klijenta da plati *kaznu* kako bi izbegao suđenje. (The lawyer advised his client to pay the fine in order to avoid a trial.)
7. Zakon propisuje različite *kazne* za različite vrste krivičnih dela. (The law prescribes different penalties for different types of criminal offenses.)
8. Policija je prekršajno prijavila vlasnika prodavnice zbog neplaćanja *kazne* za kršenje zakona o radnom vremenu. (The police filed a misdemeanor complaint against the store owner for not paying the fine for violating the law on working hours.)